author: Susan Rinkunas, Kate Lowenstein
title: Your Body Is a Disease Vector
description: People using "my body, my choice" to protest coronavirus safety guidelines are putting everyone in danger.
content: On Saturday, hundreds of people gathered at the Texas State Capitol building in Austin at a protest, organized by conspiracy theorists, to urge the state to lift its coronavirus restrictions. There were all the symbols you might expect, including pro-Trump ha… [+4446 chars]
